[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnApprox. 4 hours per week.[1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31mstart_date[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31m2014-10-16T13:00:00.000+02:00[1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31mend_date[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31m2014-12-30T13:00:00.000+01:00[1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31mstate[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31mactive[1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31mimage[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31mhttps://d1wshrh2fwv7ib.cloudfront.net/courses/027f0c75-d963-42b7-8591-598a6c055ff0/70334828151680.jpg[1;35m\"[0m[31m},{[1;35m\"[0m[31mid[1;35m\"[0m[31m:31,[1;35m\"[0m[31mtitle[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31mVehicle Dynamics II: Cornering[1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31msubtitle[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31mFrom Bugatti Veyron to Volkswagen Bettle, from racing to passenger car: learn more about cornering and drifting and look deeper into Kamm[1;35m\xE2[0m[31m[1;35m\x80[0m[31m[1;35m\x99[0m[31ms circles and Kemple[1;35m\xE2[0m[31m[1;35m\x80[0m[31m[1;35m\x99[0m[31ms diagram.[1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31mdescription[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31m####**Course Summary**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn [1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnIn this second part of Vehicle Dynamics, we will illuminate the lateral dynamic aspects of vehicles. [1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnClear and brief: the cornering of a car. [1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnIn Detail: We will start with a simple single-track model and then describe the slip angle of a wheel. The slip angle results in cornering forces, which are essential for understanding lateral dynamics. After that, we will look at the dependency between longitudinal and lateral forces using Kamm[1;35m\xE2[0m[31m[1;35m\x80[0m[31m[1;35m\x99[0m[31ms circle and Krempel[1;35m\xE2[0m[31m[1;35m\x80[0m[31m[1;35m\x99[0m[31ms diagram. Then we will investigate steady state cornering, stability and the influence of different weight distributions between inner and outer side wheels of the car. The course will finish with two applications from automotive mechatronics.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn####**What will I learn?** [1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnAt the end of the course you will [1;35m\xE2[0m[31m[1;35m\x80[0m[31m[1;35m\xA6[0m[31m[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn - understand basic principles of cornering of a car.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn - know slip angle and cornering forces.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn - understand the single track model.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn - understand the steady state cornering, stability and the influence of different weight distribution between inner and outer side of the car.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn - be able to calculate simple properties of a car.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn####**What do I have to know?**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnSome basic understanding of the following subjects will help you successfully participate in this course: Algebra; Trigonometric Functions; Differential Calculus; Linear Algebra;  Vectors; Coordinate Systems; Force, Torque, Equilibrium; Mass, Center of Gravity, Moment of Inertia; Method of Sections, Friction, Newton's Law, (Lagrange's Equation)[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn####**Workload**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn - approx. 3 hours per week plus exam preparation [1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn [1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn####**Do I get a certificate?**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn [1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnStudents participating in this course can earn the official **Statement of Participation**.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn [1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnRequirements for receiving the Statement of Participation are to participate in the final exam.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31mstart_date[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31m2014-08-19T00:00:00.000+02:00[1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31mend_date[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31m2014-12-28T00:00:00.000+01:00[1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31mstate[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31mactive[1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31mimage[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31mhttps://d1wshrh2fwv7ib.cloudfront.net/courses/d3b069bf-5cc4-4823-ba75-f698453cd0e1/70275543740080.jpg[1;35m\"[0m[31m},{[1;35m\"[0m[31mid[1;35m\"[0m[31m:305,[1;35m\"[0m[31mtitle[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31mSocial Innovation MOOC (EN)[1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31msubtitle[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31mSocial Innovations change the rules by which people live together. Learn what social innovations are and how they can be developed. Because the way we live, work and do business could actually be quite different![1;35m\"[0m[31m,[1;35m\"[0m[31mdescription[1;35m\"[0m[31m:[1;35m\"[0m[31m####**Course Summary**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnSocial innovations, i.e. new social practices, are everywhere and largely influence our lives: they change the rules of the game in business, civil society and politics. With social innovations we can design social practices that are more beneficial, sustainable or just.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnBut what are social innovations? And what effects can they have? This course is an introduction to the topic. You will gain an overview of what social innovations are, how they function and how they can be developed.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn####**What do I learn?**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnYou will learn what social innovations are and understand how they can help solve societal problems. You will get an overview of important literature and debates on social innovation. [1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnYou will get to know and apply methods to develop, implement, and scale social innovations. Exercises will allow you to apply the methods, develop own ideas and gather first-hand experiences.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn####**What do I need to know?**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnThis is an introductory course. Previous knowledge is not required. The course is designed for people interested in understanding and/or designing societal change.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn####**Course Structure**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn**Chapter 1: A New Innovation Paradigm**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnIn this chapter you will learn what [1;35m\xE2[0m[31m[1;35m\x80[0m[31m[1;35m\x9C[0m[31msocial innovation[1;35m\xE2[0m[31m[1;35m\x80[0m[31m[1;35m\x9D[0m[31m means. You will get an overview of how social innovations can be developed and implemented. Also, we explain the differences between all the [1;35m\xE2[0m[31m[1;35m\x80[0m[31m[1;35m\x9C[0m[31msocial[1;35m\xE2[0m[31m[1;35m\x80[0m[31m[1;35m\x9D[0m[31m something-concepts like social business, social entrepreneurship, and corporate social responsibilities.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn**Chapter 2: The Spectrum of Social Innovation**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnThere are different forms and formats of social innovation. Gain an overview of the variety of social innovations in this chapter. Specifically, you learn about social innovations that origin in civil society, business, and the social sector. Moreover, you will learn about cross-sector social innovations.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn**Chapter 3: Broaden your Horizon: Questioning the Existing and Recognizing Challenges**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnSocial innovators see opportunities where others see problems. Learn to change your perspective in order to recognize opportunities to solve societal problems with social innovations.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn**Chapter 4: Designing and Implementing Social Innovations: Tools**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnDesign Thinking and Lean Start-up will help you to design social innovations together with your (future) beneficiaries. Furthermore, you learn how you can convince others by using effective storytelling.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn**Chapter 5: Designing and Implementing Social Innovations: Learning from Others**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnYou will learn how others developed and implemented social innovations and how they learned to overcome resistance. Also, you learn about typical mechanisms of social value creation.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn**Chapter 6: Impact and Vision**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnIn this chapter you learn how to analyse the impact of social innovations and how you can increase the impact of social innovations using specific strategies of scaling and replication. Also, our experts will provide some suggestions and tips for future social innovators.[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn####**Workload**[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mn[1;35m\\[0m[31mr[1;35m\\[0m[31mnApproximately 4 hours per week for watching video lectures, taking quizzes and completing homework assignments. 